snippet.title: Forgotten Hope 2 - Leaning Feature
snippet.description:
Welcome back to another Forgotten Hope 2 update! 

This time we are showcasing you a little taster of things to come in our next public release of Forgotten Hope 2, introducing the "Leaning" function. 

Hope you enjoyed this little teaser, come back again next time for more news!

Play Forgotten Hope 2 for free: https://playfh2.net/
